### Reservation Endpoints

### Check availability (Public - no authentication required)
POST {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/check-availability
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "roomId": 1,
  "startTime": "2025-01-15T09:00:00Z",
  "endTime": "2025-01-15T10:00:00Z"
}

###

### Get all reservations (Protected - requires authentication)
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get all reservations with filters (Protected - requires authentication)
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations?roomId=1&startDate=2025-01-01T00:00:00Z&endDate=2025-01-31T23:59:59Z
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get reservation by ID (Protected - requires authentication)
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/1
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

###

### Get my reservations (Protected - requires authentication)
GET {{baseUri}}/api/reservations/my
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}

